HEADWORD: Infante
<hw>In*fan"te</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp. & Pg. See
<er>Infant</er>.]</ety> <def>A title given to every one of sons of the
kings of Spain and Portugal, except the eldest or heir
apparent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Infanthood</ent>⟦br⟧
